name: Any Letter Name Print (Vintage Map)
description:
This is a print of the Letter A with your choice of name written below. Great for nurseries or kids rooms.At checkout send me a message with the letter and name you would like.

****This listing is for ANY letter****

Paper size is 8.3" x 11.7" (21cm x 29.7cm)

The map used in this print is a vintage one from 1950's atlas.

It is printed on a lovely Matte Heavyweight Epson paper using Claria Inks. I experimented with many different papers and inks before I settled on this one.

It is a bright white, ultra smooth coated paper with a lovely texture. The bright heavyweight white matte coating provides a non glare surface for vivid colours with extra clarity for minimal reflection.

It is archival for up to 98 years under glass in a frame
and the colours have a lush richness.

All prints are signed and dated by the artist, and arrive sealed in a cello sleeve and a protective stiff envelope.

I use Airmail to send all my art. It will be posted in a well protected package with the artwork itself in a cello bag with two pieces of board to keep it flat.

I am very particular with keeping things nice and flat and ensuring its safe delivery to you.

I ship to anywhere in the world.

Thankyou for visiting my shop!
